			    <HR color=#000000 SIZE=-1>
			  	Every commander has a chance to survive battles.<br />
<br />
Some races have bonus or commander survival penalty. There's also 2 devices that increase survival chances.<br />
<br />
Bosalian: +10 commander survival<br />
Buckaneer: +5 commander survival<br />
Human :    +5 commander survival<br />
<br />
Agerus :  -10 commander survival<br />
Xeloss :   -5 commander survival<br />
Targoid :  -5 commander survival (Clonal double- targoid commander ability raises it's own chances of survival by 90 at lv20, making him almost unkillable)<br />
<br />
Devices<br />
Homing Beacon (lv4): +10 commander survival<br />
Escape Pod    (lv3): +20 commander survival<br />
<br />
It is weird that the best of the 2 is the lv3 one instead of the lv4 device.			   <P align=right></P>
